  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Aspects </strong><em>celestial, fire, soul</em></p><hr /><p>The lost sorcerous power of a former celestial sorceress, slowly rekindled as she struggles to come to terms with her new life as a vampire and a cleric.</p><hr /><p><strong>Set Items: </strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.PJboj72eI9JXjtbn]{Bladed Gauntlet (Staff)} (1st Level), @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.tH5GirEy7YB3ZgCk]{+1 Silver Striking Rapier} (6th Level), @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.XeiuCRFzxHA7mm0X]{Endless Grimoire (Greater)} (10th Level), @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.wbxLKvA46AfoFU0h]{Ring of Magic (Type IV)} (14th Level),</p><hr /><p><strong>Gifts: </strong>The set grants the following gifts.</p><ul><li><p><em>1</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.P4Byw03ZPr2DRAHh]{Flare Bolt}</p></li><li><p><em>2</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.tcdAGUg7A8pN9reB]{Divine Retribution}</p></li><li><p><em>3</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.mHwOh6WmbmL16L1t]{Cleanse Soul}</p></li><li><p><em>4</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.CJTMvOWLdM5RN2jH]{Searing Wave}</p></li><li><p><em>5</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-relics.relic-gifts.Item.9vwEfAr45x9Ypkg4]{Soul Magic}</p></li></ul><hr /><p><strong>Collective Features: </strong>The set grants the following features.</p><ul><li><p><em>Two Items</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.beCUvesxgARNK5kc]{Flare Bolt} does 1d8 fire damage per relic level.</p></li><li><p><em>Three Items</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.BnsEMw6aMbugwba3]{Divine Retribution} deals two additional dice instead of one.</p></li><li><p><em>Four Items</em>: You can use @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.kbcqzJpIu6Y2za6w]{Cleanse Soul} once per hour, and the status bonus to saving throws against curses increases to +3.</p></li><li><p><em>Five Items</em>: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-misc.our-items.Item.wOH0aTFLnsZls2xK]{Searing Wave} only damages enemies.</p></li></ul>"
    },
